article.headline: TCU 62, Colgate 37
article.story: FORT WORTH, Texas -- Kevin Langford scored 20 points and pulled down 11 rebounds to lead TCU to a 62-37 victory over Colgate on Tuesday. Ronnie Moss was the only other player to score in double figures for the Horned Frogs (8-5) with 18 points. Ben Johnson led Colgate (3-8) with 13 points. TCU held Colgate to just 10 points in the second half after being down 27-26 at halftime. The Horned Frogs outscored the Raiders 32-8 with points in the paint.
